						 <p>The 7 train was a fun pick, it's such a weird line that this seems rather plausible for an anomaly.</p> <p>That said, I found the clinical tone, escalation, and audio logs in particular to be very lacking. There wasn't much cohesion and it failed to keep my interest throughout. -1</p> 
